name: .ZFSENDTOTARGET File Extension
summary: Learn about .ZFSENDTOTARGET files and view a list of programs that open them.

description: Zipped file created by right-clicking a file or folder in Windows and selecting Send To→Compressed Folder; can be decompressed by Windows or decompression program.

content: This feature is available in Windows XP and can be enabled in Windows Me by selecting "Add/Remove Programs→Windows Setup→System Tools→Compressed Folders."
ZFSENDTOTARGET files apply to Windows Me and later.
